    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="lead">1.What is this notice?</span></p>
<p>This is the ‘Casual Worker Privacy Notice’ of Queen Margaret University.  Our contact details are: <a href="mailto:HRGDPR@qmu.ac.uk" title="Hr Email Address">Hr Email Address</a></p>
<p>We are a data ‘controller’, which means we are responsible for deciding how we hold and use your personal information. This notice explains how and why we will collect and use your personal information in the context of your engagement with us and your rights in relation to your personal information.</p>]]></Value>
